---
title: Open-Faced Bruschetta & Burrata Sandwich with Roasted Potato Wedges
description: We've taken the classic Italian antipasto and made it a meal for two! Grilled bread is brushed with garlic oil and topped with creamy burrata, juicy tomatoes and fresh basil. A final drizzle of balsamic glaze and you're all set for date night!
